---
import { Markdown } from "astro/components";

import MainHead from "../components/MainHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer/index.jsx";
import Nav from "../components/Nav/index.jsx";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <MainHead title="About | Chaviea Cleveland" />
    <style lang="scss">
      .heroImg { object-fit: cover; img { width: 100%; height: 100%; } } .bio {
      font-size: var(--f-u1); line-height: 2; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Nav />
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1>About Chaviea</h1>
      <div class="heroImg">
        <img
          width="1400"
          height="350"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1456086272160-b28b0645b729?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&h=350&q=75" />
      </div>

      <div class="bio wrapper wrapper__readable mt8">
        <Markdown>
          Hello! I'm a design student studying graphic design in the hopes of
          one day designing delightful customer facing products. I have a
          **passion** for the small details and love making engaging imagery. No
          matter the medium I look to excell at creating rich viisuals to tell a
          brand's story.
        </Markdown>

        <p>
          Other than designing the brands of tomorrow I _love_ styling my hair
          and makeup in new and interesting ways. I also am <span style="color: #f971b0;font-weight: bold;"
            >obsessed</span> with <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/glizzychampions/">my puppers</a
          >.
        </p>

        <Markdown>
          If you're interested in hiring me to help craft you brand, please dont
          hesitate to [reach out to me](mailto:chavcleveland71@gmail.com) ❤️
        </Markdown>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
